title: Carson Wentz Contract with JLC, Zach Ertz Interview (Football 6/7)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by CBS Sports NFL Insider Jason La Canfora to talk about Carson Wentz' new contract, the Baltimore Ravens OTAs and Trent Williams holdout from the Redskins. Then Will is joined by Eagles tight end Zach Ertz to talk about US Women's World Cup Soccer and the 2019 Eagles season (recorded before the Wentz contract, FYI).
